model.fsa.ver1
Class Automaton

java.lang.Object
  model.fsa.FSAPublisherAdaptor
      model.fsa.ver1.Automaton
All Implemented Interfaces:
Cloneable, Annotable, DESModel, FSAModel, FSAPublisher
public class Automaton
extends FSAPublisherAdaptor
implements Cloneable, FSAModel

This class is the topmost class in the automaton hierarchy. It serves as the datastructure for states, transitions and events, and gives access to data iterators that are customized to maintain data integrity of the automaton at all times.

Author:
Axel Gottlieb Michelsen, Kristian Edlund, Lenko Grigorov
